働省による検査抑制策の誤りを認めますか。根本的に清算し、国の責任による大規模検査の…", "…る検査抑制策の誤りを認めますか。根本的に清算し、国の責任による大規模検査の推進へかじを切るべきではないか。お答えください。全国の保健所は、自…", "…半分に減らされました。その結果、感染拡大の際に保健所の業務が逼迫し、検査で陽性と判定された人に保健所からの連絡すら届かず、自宅で重症化するな…"]}]}]}, {"date": "2021-12-17", "meeting": [{"meeting_name": "参議院 予算委員会", "remarks": [{"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/337", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/339", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/341", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/343", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/345", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/349", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/351", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/353", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/355", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/357", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/359", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/361", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/363", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/365", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/367", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/369", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/371", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/373", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/375", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/377", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120715261X00220211217/